{"tid":2461005,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭手足突圍理大被控暴動 杜麗冰拒保釋申請","createTime":"2021-03-25T07:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T11:08:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba9380a2cef00998c7e0d3ec0acfd49b57b55d1","tid":2461005,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14618&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=da6bd98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14618</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第一庭 <br />\n#杜麗冰法官 <br />\n#申請保釋<br />\n#1118理大 <br />\n<br />\nD7: 鄭(22) 🛑已還押13日<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n暴動<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n被控於2019年11月18日，在香港理工大學外暢運道連同其他人參與暴動<br />\n<br />\n申請方(辯方)代表： #藍凱欣大律師<br />\n答辯方(控方)代表：Ms Wong<br />\n<br />\n1429 開庭<br />\n申請方/辯方已就補充文件索取指示，答辯方/控方指已再呈上更清晰放大版及另呈上多一補充文件<br />\n<br />\n（按：又擠牙膏式呈上文件，既然都遲就點解唔今朝一次過）<br />\n<br />\n1441 申請方申請押後以索取進一步指示<br />\n<br />\n1457 開庭<br />\n申請方/辯方已就(再)補充文件(再)索取指示<br />\n法官直斥答辯方/控方準備得好差<br />\n<br />\n1512<br />\n‼️保釋被拒‼️<br />\n<br />\n- - - <br />\n礙於香港法例對報導保釋法律程序的限制，被指稱為暴徒的我好冇骨氣地無力在此覆述本聆訊內容。就此致歉🙏🏻"},{"pid":"d16c3e762bff822691e801831b4925142f743ce4","tid":2461005,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f827d7f5b49b5588e304fbda465662c56c03382","tid":2461005,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91641410eab5b5c8fd0ad