" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54da247d68cbb597114625a4db7b86986cf9141b","tid":2461005,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:30:18.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）29人早前被警方分批起訴，涉嫌於前年11月「理大圍城」事件中參與暴動，其中一名被告、應屆大學畢業生今（25日）向高等法院申請保釋。《國安法》指定法官杜麗冰考慮雙方陳詞後，最終拒絕其保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n開庭前紥馬尾、架着黑框眼鏡的鄭步出囚室，與友人和親友對視即觸動情緒，雙眼通紅。控辯雙方進行陳詞期間，鄭沒有戴上耳機，一直專心地聆聽律師與法官英語對談內容，一度集中得皺起眉頭。<br />\n<br />\n鄭聽到結果後表現平靜，與旁聽人士及家屬揮手告別。其母親及數名友人離庭後難以接受結果，不禁流淚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081669&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fqe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=10e7d3e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081669&h=b5556908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081669</a>"},{"pid":"6d65d966e70eaa28449b5d907541571b0ce630b9","tid":2461005,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e296c4db3b1c6b91251223306b393695c6a5c147","tid":2461005,"uid":39503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5c23d960e08432f8cf7fc8f3676319daee3c2c","tid":2461005,"uid":1414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"係入面安心休養，我地會記住你嘅付出"},{"pid":"d201f510c6458bceae4cf4c26f1315dbe048168d","tid":2461005,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=